        <pre><code>&lt;link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css"&gt;</code></pre>
    </p>

    <h2 class="js-question">How to Use JavaScript in a Webpage</h2>
    <p class="js-question">
        To link external JS:
        <pre><code>&lt;script src="script.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</code></pre>
        To write JS within HTML:
        <pre><code>&lt;script&gt;alert('Hello World!');&lt;/script&gt;</code></pre>
